item.title: The Platinum-certified album debuted at #4 on the Billboard 200 and spawned the Top 5 hit ‘Work From Home’ which was ranked as the 14th best girl group song of all time by Billboard.

item.title: The second single off his sophomore album ‘Beauty Behind the Madness’ became a #1 hit on the Billboard Hot 100 and a Top 3 in the UK. It has amassed over 1.8 billion streams on Spotify and is certified 11x Platinum in the US.
